<p align="left" style="text-align: left;"><span>2016</span><span>年、</span><span>2017</span><span>年、</span><span>2018</span><span>年、</span><span>2019</span><span>年、</span><span>2020</span><span>年</span><span>1-6</span><span>月，恒辉安防实现归属于母公司所有者的净利润分别为</span><span>4615.49</span><span>万元、</span><span>3664.00</span><span>万元、</span><span>7186.21</span><span>万元、</span><span>9684.89</span><span>万元、</span><span>5871.89</span><span>万元；经营活动产生的现金流量净额分别为</span><span>3753.04</span><span>万元、</span><span>5208.62</span><span>万元、</span><span>7564.54</span><span>万元、</span><span>1.22</span><span>亿元、</span><span>6413.50</span><span>万元。</span></p>
<p><span>2016</span><span>年、</span><span>2017</span><span>年、</span><span>2018</span><span>年、</span><span>2019</span><span>年、</span><span>2020</span><span>年</span><span>1-6</span><span>月，恒辉安防加权平均净资产收益率分别为</span><span>29.83%</span><span>、</span><span>20.90%</span><span>、</span><span>30.87%</span><span>、</span><span>28.52%</span><span>、</span><span>14.07%</span><span>。</span></p>
